vsan.iscsi.action.edit.incoming.secret.w:
Incoming CHAP secret must be:
12 to 16 characters in length;
Minimum 1 uppercase character;
Minimum 1 lowercase character;
Minimum 1 numeric digit;
Minimum 1 special character (!, @, #, $, %, &, ^ and *);
 Only visible ASCII characters including space (excluding non-printing control characters such as BEL, Nul, ...).

